        <p>
          The human brain is the most powerful organ in the known universe — yet most people never truly
          understand how it works or how to use it to its full potential. At <strong>Bhāva Tech</strong>,
          we help children, students, and adults do exactly that.
        </p>
        <p style="margin-top:14px;">
          Through scientifically designed IQ, EQ, and SQ assessments, we give you a clear picture of where
          your cognitive strengths lie and where improvement is possible. Our Brain Gym programs train the
          mind the same way physical exercise trains the body — with consistency, structure, and measurable
          results. <strong>All services are available 100% online for global participants.</strong>
        </p>
        <ul class="highlight-list">
          <li>🧠 Understand your IQ, EQ &amp; SQ with certified assessments</li>
          <li>🏋️ Train your brain with structured Brain Gym programs</li>
          <li>🧘 Restore focus and calm in our Meditational Lab</li>
          <li>📊 Receive detailed personal reports with actionable guidance</li>
          <li>🌍 Online sessions available for students worldwide</li>
          <li>🏢 Physical office at Ramatalkies, Visakhapatnam</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- RIGHT: Visual Stats Cards -->
      <div class="about-visual section-animate" style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:20px;">

        <div style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1a1a5e,#2d2d8f); border-radius:16px; padding:28px 24px; text-align:center; box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);">
