          </div>
          <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12); border-radius:14px; padding:22px 16px; text-align:center;">
            <div style="font-size:2rem; font-weight:700; color:#34d399;">🧘</div>
            <div style="font-size:0.82rem; color:#aab4d4; margin-top:6px;">Meditation Lab</div>
          </div>
          <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12); border-radius:14px; padding:22px 16px; text-align:center;">
