    <div style="background:#fff; border-radius:16px; padding:36px; margin-bottom:40px;
                box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.07); border-left:5px solid #6c5ce7;">
      <h3 style="font-size:1.5rem; color:#0d2b55; margin-bottom:8px;">🏆 Our Activities & Why They Matter</h3>
      <p style="color:#666; font-size:0.95rem; margin-bottom:24px;">
        Every activity in our Brain Gym program is purpose-built with a specific cognitive development goal:
      </p>
      <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(260px,1fr)); gap:20px;">

        <div style="background:#f8f9ff; border-radius:12px; padding:20px; border-top:3px solid #6c5ce7;">
          <div style="font-size:1.8rem;">🎮</div>
          <h4 style="color:#0d2b55; margin:10px 0 6px;">Gamified Exercises</h4>
          <p style="color:#555; font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.6;"><strong>Why it matters:</strong> Game-based learning triggers dopamine release, making the brain more receptive, motivated, and willing to repeat challenges. Children learn 40% faster when content is gamified.</p>
        </div>

        <div style="background:#f8f9ff; border-radius:12px; padding:20px; border-top:3px solid #6c5ce7;">
          <div style="font-size:1.8rem;">🧩</div>
          <h4 style="color:#0d2b55; margin:10px 0 6px;">Memory & Recall Training</h4>
          <p style="color:#555; font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.6;"><strong>Why it matters:</strong> Hippocampal memory circuits are strengthened through progressive recall games — directly improving academic retention, exam performance, and working memory capacity.</p>
        </div>

        <div style="background:#f8f9ff; border-radius:12px; padding:20px; border-top:3px solid #6c5ce7;">
          <div style="font-size:1.8rem;">🎯</div>
          <h4 style="color:#0d2b55; margin:10px 0 6px;">Attention & Focus Drills</h4>
          <p style="color:#555; font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.6;"><strong>Why it matters:</strong> Timed concentration tasks train the anterior cingulate cortex — the brain's attention control center — improving sustained focus, impulse control, and task completion.</p>
        </div>

        <div style="background:#f8f9ff; border-radius:12px; padding:20px; border-top:3px solid #6c5ce7;">
          <div style="font-size:1.8rem;">🌿</div>
          <h4 style="color:#0d2b55; margin:10px 0 6px;">Mindfulness Activities</h4>
          <p style="color:#555; font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.6;"><strong>Why it matters:</strong> Body-scan meditations and breath awareness reduce cortisol (stress hormone), calm the amygdala (fear center), and create a calm, alert state ideal for deep learning.</p>
        </div>

        <div style="background:#f8f9ff; border-radius:12px; padding:20px; border-top:3px solid #6c5ce7;">
          <div style="font-size:1.8rem;">📈</div>
          <h4 style="color:#0d2b55; margin:10px 0 6px;">Progress Tracking</h4>
          <p style="color:#555; font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.6;"><strong>Why it matters:</strong> Regular benchmarking shows measurable cognitive growth — motivating children, guiding parents, and allowing us to adapt the program to each child's unique development pace.</p>
        </div>

        <div style="background:#f8f9ff; border-radius:12px; padding:20px; border-top:3px solid #6c5ce7;">
          <div style="font-size:1.8rem;">📋</div>
          <h4 style="color:#0d2b55; margin:10px 0 6px;">Parent Report Card</h4>
          <p style="color:#555; font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.6;"><strong>Why it matters:</strong> Transparent, detailed weekly reports keep parents informed about cognitive improvements, behavioral changes, and recommended home reinforcement activities.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
